<h2 class="api_method_name" data-subtopic="Calendar Events" name="method.calendar_events_api.set_course_timetable">
<a href="#method.calendar_events_api.set_course_timetable" name="method.calendar_events_api.set_course_timetable">
      Set a course timetable
    </a>
<span class="defined-in"><a href="https://github.com/instructure/canvas-lms/blob/master/app/controllers/calendar_events_api_controller.rb">CalendarEventsApiController#set_course_timetable</a></span>
</h2>
<h3 class="beta">BETA: This API endpoint is not finalized, and there could be breaking changes before its final release.</h3>
<h3 class="endpoint">
    POST /api/v1/courses/:course_id/calendar_events/timetable
  </h3>
<p>Creates and updates âtimetableâ events for a course. Can automaticaly
generate a series of calendar events based on simple schedules (e.g.
âMonday and Wednesday at 2:00pmâ )</p>
<p>Existing timetable events for the course and course sections will be
updated if they still are part of the timetable. Otherwise, they will be
deleted.</p>
